Adrenaline GTS 17
Features


1

BIOMOGO DNA MIDSOLE CUSHIONING
						dynamically adapts to every step and stride.
					


2

PROGRESSIVE DIAGONAL ROLL BAR
						guides the body back into its natural motion path
					


3

FULL-LENGTH SEGMENTED CRASH PAD
						accommodates any foot landing and delivers smooth heel-to-toe transitions
					


4

UPDATED V-GROOVE
						create a more natural release for a soft, smooth feel underfoot
					


5

CONFORMABLE SADDLE W/ ADJUSTABLE EYELETS
						pulls from the heel to wrap the midfoot in a secure fit
					















